quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  56,39,Likuga lyejinji (lya ŵa kunkono wan’dyo) lichityochela mu ŵandu ŵandanda
  56,40,Nambo soni likuga lyejinji (lya ŵa kunkono wan’dyo) lichityochela mu ŵandu ŵakumalichisya
  56,41,"Ni (pachiŵa pana) ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji, ana ŵandu ŵa kunkono wanchiji ni ŵapi (kusakala kwao kuchiŵa uli)"
  56,42,"(Tachiŵa) mu chimbunga chamoto, ni mesi gamasemule nnope"
  56,43,Ni m’bulili wa lyosi lyepiliwu nnope
  56,44,Wangapeleka kusisimila namuno kutulalila
  56,45,Chisimu ŵanganyao nkaniyiŵe yalakweyi (ku duniya) ŵaliji nkutama umi wakusangalala (ni yakanyisyidwa)
  56,46,Ni ŵaliji nkwendelechela (kutenda) sambi syekulungwa
  56,47,"Ni ŵaliji nkuŵecheta kuti: “Ana patuchiwapo ni kusyuka litaka ni maupa, nambo yakuona uwwe tuchiukulidwa (m’malembe)?”"
  56,48,“Ni achatati ŵetu ŵakwe ŵandanda?”
  56,49,"Jilani (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ): “Chisimu ŵandanda ni ŵambesi ŵakwe.”"
  56,50,“Tachisonganganyisyidwa wa kunsongangano wetomechedwe wa lisiku lyakumanyika.”
  56,51,"“Kaneka chisimu ŵanganyammwe, E jenumanja ŵalupuso, (soni) ŵakanila!”"
  56,52,“Tinkalye kwene chitela cha Zakkum.”
  56,53,“Ni tinkachigumbasyeje ndumbo (syenu).”
  56,54,“Ni tinkachimweleje mesi gamasemule nnope.”
  56,55,“Ni tinkamweje mwasikumwelaga ngamiya syanjota nnope.”
  56,56,Aji ni mbiiko jao Lisiku Lyamalipilo
  56,57,"Uwwe twan’gumbile jenumanja, nambi ligongo chichi ngankukulupilila (ya kwimuka m’malembe panyuma pakuwa)"
  56,58,Ana nkuliona uli lindondwa lya ulume lyankudondechesyaga (m’chiŵelechelo)
  56,59,"Ana jenumanja niŵankuligumbaga (kuti liŵe mundu), kapena Uwwe niŵatukuligumbaga"
  56,60,"Uwwe tupimiile chilikati chenu chiwa (kuti jwalijose mwa jenumanja tachiwa), ni nganituŵa Uwwe ŵakulepela"
  56,61,"Kuti chitun’galawusye kagumbidwe kenu (lisiku lya Kiyama), nikun’gumba mu kaŵe kangankukamanyilila"
  56,62,"Soni chisimu chene pamasile pankumanyi gumba kwandanda (kuti Allah ni juŵagumbile), nambi uli ngankukumbuchila (yanti Jwalakwe mpaka jukombole gumba kwaŵili)"
  56,63,Ana nkujiona uli mbeju jankupandaga
  56,64,"Ana jenumanja niŵankujimesyaga, kapena Uwwe niŵatukumesyaga"
  56,65,"Tungasache tungajitesile kuŵa jakuteketuka, ni nkaliji ŵakusimonga (chachintendesye kuti jiteketuche)"
  56,66,"(Ni nkatiji): “Chisimu uwwe tugambile kwasa chipanje chetu.”"
  56,67,“Nambo uwwe tujimidwe.”
  56,68,Ana nkugaona uli mesi gankumwaga
  56,69,"Ana jenumanja ni ŵan’gatulwisye kuumila kumawunde gawula, kapena Uwwe ni Akutulsya"
  56,70,"Tungasache tungagatesile kuŵa gachijete nnope, nambi ligongo chichi ngankutogolela"
  56,71,Ana nkuuwona uli moto wankukolesyaga
  56,72,"Ana jenumanja ni ŵamwagumbile itela yakwe, kapena Uwwe ni Akugumba"
  56,73,"Uwwe tuwutesile walakwe (motowo) kuŵa chikumbusyo (cha Moto wa ku Akhera), ni wakwakamuchisya ŵa paulendo"
  56,74,Basi liswejesyani lina lya Ambuje ŵenu Ŵakulungwa nnope (Allah)